{"tid":928140,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【龍床盤開售】菁雋周六賣27伙 佔首張價單不足四成","createTime":"2018-12-04T15:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T15:37:14.000Z","uid":174649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f24bd30f83a0b9a5ca33f0c568faccd300dec5f","tid":928140,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181204/large/1543925340_37ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181204%2Flarge%2F1543925340_37ad.jpg&h=e7f1dcbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以貴絕屯門區登場的「龍床盤」菁雋剛公佈銷售安排，本周六(8日)發售27伙，佔首張價單73伙的37%。消息指，項目今日再增加一個認購登記，<strong>過去六天共收59票，連地產代理都話收票慘淡</strong>。本周四截止認購登記。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2ca6582de7c9c6f76a0d9aa6d6acb7a7c6f705","tid":928140,"uid":57490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"比狗住都嫌細啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd90adb168b1ca344012c167e0a7de080f87aa23","tid":928140,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"淨係賣27伙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21a6971c66b5bf5428c0ed8221b7a1123f21c67","tid":928140,"uid":93321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd90adb168b1ca344012c167e0a7de080f87aa23","tid":928140,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"淨係賣27伙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.